name: 0.9.4 (alpha)
body:
0.9.4 marks the launch of developer tools. We've also added Ethlance, Dentacoin & CommitETH as default contacts.

Learn more about this release [here](https://blog.status.im/status-0-9-4-trufflebox-embark-plugin-ethlance-dentacoin-commiteth-dbc040dd554d).

name: 0.9.3 (alpha)
body:
0.9.3 includes [38 bug fixes](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues?q=is%3Aissue+is%3Aclosed+label%3Abug+milestone%3A0.9.3), along with compatibility with Melonport, Gnosis, Firstblood and bchat.

Learn more about this release [here](https://blog.status.im/status-0-9-3-melonport-gnosis-firstblood-bchat-79b4ee85f2fe).

name: 0.9.0 (alpha)
body: Status' first public alpha release. For the first time, you can browse DApps on Android & iOS and have a mobile Ethereum node in your pocket.
